类 Speed

  org.crosswire.jsword.book.test.Speed

java.lang.Runnable
public class Speed
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

Speed is a simple benchmark that tests how fast a version is. The current set of tasks that we perform are rather arbitrary. But that is something that we can improve on when we have more usage information.
